      <div xml:id="NA193-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu piriviṭai āṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaḷ (ET: vāṭaikkuc) colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what SHE said who was unable to bear it in the time of separation.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA193">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            aṭṭarak kuruviṉ vaṭṭumukai yīṅkait</l>
<l>            tuyttalaip putumalart tuḷittalaik kalāva</l>
<l>            niṟainīrp puṉiṟṟup pulantuḻaii yāṉā</l>
<l>            yirumpulan taḻūum peruntaṇ vāṭai</l>
<l>            niṉakkut tītaṟin taṉṟō vilamē </l>
<l>            paṇaittō ḷelvaḷai ñekiḻttaveṅ kātala</l>
<l>            raruñceyaṟ poruṭpiṇip pirintaṉa rāka</l>
<l>            yārumi loruciṟai yiruntu</l>
<l>            pēraña ruṟuviyai varuttā tīmē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O great cool north wind that encircles the vast fields,</l>
<l>you unendingly stirring the field for what is newly generated</l>
<l rend="indent4">                in the full water,</l>
<l rend="indent">            so that the tops of the cotton-headed new blossoms are perturbed</l>
<l rend="indent">             by drops on the mimosa with buds as round</l>
<l rend="indent2">            as the colour(?) of molten(?) lacquer,</l>
<l>– nothing evil against you has been known to us.<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">aṟintaṉṟō ilamē</term>: for the same type of construction cf. NA 175.6 (see also note on NA 27.6). The above translation ignores the -<term xml:lang="ta">ō</term> which makes matters more complicated still perhaps thus: "as for evil being known of towards you, not with regard to us."</note></l>
<l>Don't make suffer the one who [already] has big grief<note place="foot">Here we either have to take it, with T.V.G., that SHE talks of herself in the 3rd person, or that, for once, the <term xml:lang="ta">kiḷavi</term> is not correct in attributing speech to HER, while it really is the confidante.</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            being on one side where there is nobody,</l>
<l rend="indent">            since our lover who has made loose the light bangles on [her]</l>
<l rend="indent3">                 bamboo arms</l>
<l rend="indent">            has separated enticed by wealth difficult to make.</l>
         </lg>
